evelopment Project, and partly financed by equity from the sponsors and debt capital by a number of institutional investors in the United States and Europe.\"}]', '<p>Our experience in the Nigerian Oil & Gas and Financial sectors is vast and varied. We have successfully advised firms, financial institutions, energy conglomerates and multinationals on several projections and transactions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Below are some relevant experiences garnered over the years.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-11-17 13:15:13', '2015-11-17 13:53:43', 'f826d620-bdc2-4e26-b63d-2b9e95918f19');
