acility.\"},{\"col1\":\"Conducted legal due diligence and provided pre-investment advice in a $15 million USD private equity investment by African Capital Alliance in Bankers Warehouse Limited foremost international private equity firm in a leading cash-in-transit company in Nigeria.\"},{\"col1\":\"Represented Baker Hughes in several litigation matters in the Niger-Delta region and other parts of Nigeria.\"},{\"col1\":\"Represented ExxonMobil in litigation matters in the Niger-Delta region of Nigeria.\"},{\"col1\":\"Represented a multi-national oil service company in various labour disputes including actions at the High Courts in the Niger-Delta region.\"},{\"col1\":\"Advising and assisting a multi-national company in respect of a tax dispute with the Lagos State Board of Internal Revenue.\"}]', '[{\"col1\":\"\"}]', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '2015-11-17 18:22:08', '2015-11-17 18:28:25', '69935a19-0839-4c75-aabd-a0f1d61682fd');
